      "content": "the \"quiet end of the pain\"... that's exactly it. it feels like the only way to actually stop the noise in my head. everyone keeps saying \"it gets better\" or \"time heals,\" but i don't want time. i just want the emptiness to stop. it feels so heavy, like i'm just dragging this shell of a life around for no reason.",
